# This file contains only npm-compatible settings. The pnpm-only supply-chain
# hardening (minimumReleaseAge etc.) lives in pnpm-workspace.yaml — the only
# non-npmrc file pnpm reads settings from — so an `npm install` of this
# package does not print "Unknown config" warnings on every invocation.
# Audit #36: previously these settings lived here and tripped npm's strict
# .npmrc reader; a follow-up parked them in a `.pnpmrc` file that pnpm never
# reads (removed).
